room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by The Escape Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
room_address: 200 S. Meridian St., Suite 220 Indianapolis, IN 46225
room_description:
As a leading national expert on biological pathogens, your team has been assembled in hopes of avoiding a national outbreak of the dangerous virus. On arriving at the abandoned lab, half of your team was immediately accosted by another infected victim who had been hiding in the lab.
The historical research on the disease indicates its effects may be reversible within a short window of being infected. It was even rumored that a cure for this disease was in the lab, but it was never found. Can you find the cure for you and your team before the disease and its effects are permanent?
